untangle-archive-keyring (5.0.2-1) current; urgency=medium

  * Add bookworm signing key (untangle-archive-bookworm-automatic.gpg)
    to trusted.gpg.d (NGFW-15626).
  * Add trixie signing key (untangle-archive-trixie-automatic.asc) to
    trusted.gpg.d. ASCII-armored because trixie apt uses sqv (Sequoia
    OpenPGP) which rejects keybox-format .gpg keyrings (NGFW-15749).
  * Pre-stages trust so customers upgrading from bullseye to bookworm
    or trixie do not need manual keyring intervention before flipping
    apt sources.

